    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Spacetime)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 11 (Spell Level 6)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 27 | <b>Successes:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 15 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 31</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob, S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You disappear in a flash of yellow Chakra and instantly appear in a square adjacent to a creature of your choice that is carrying your Shikei no In. When you arrive, you can make a hide check as a free action to attempt to remain undetected.</p>\n\n\n\n",
